# Densitas line-ending policy.
# The editing-environment mount rewrites .cmd files to CRLF while they are
# stored LF in the repo, which produced perpetual "modified" churn on
# build.cmd / start.cmd. Pin Windows batch scripts to CRLF in the working
# tree, LF in the repo, so the churn stops for good.
*.cmd text eol=crlf
*.bat text eol=crlf
